						<div class="postbody">Put 00FF in the address box of the add breakpoint dialog, then check the "write" box. 
<br />
<br />In your code, add an sta $FF before the routine you want to check.
<br />
<br />Edit: Forgot to say, that's a pretty great idea, Tokumaru. I always just used to use odd opcodes.</div>

