					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">As long as This is a set value and not a RAM location, 2 will not work and 3 will. If This is a RAM value, neither will work as you just can't do that. And remember, since that's a word sized pointer, you may be needing to do +2 to move to the next pointer, keep that in mind! <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" /></div>

